    |    |                      | "Control.Monad.STM"              |                                       |
    +----+----------------------+--------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
    | 11 | __Chunked bodies__   |                                                                          |
    +----+----------------------+                                                                          |
    | 12 | __Request parsing__  |                                                                          |
    +----+----------------------+                                                                          |
    | 13 | __Reading headers__  |                                                                          |
    +----+----------------------+                 The remaining chapters are in progress.                  |
